bsetroot

NOTE: pypanel does NOT like backgrounds set by bsetroot

(getting a bsetroot binary the ugly way)

Download blackbox-0.70.0beta2.tar.gz from SourceForge
http://prdownloads.sourceforge.net/blackboxwm/blackbox-0.70.0beta2.tar.gz

Unpack the archive

# cd blackbox-0.70.0beta2
# ./configure
# make
# cd util
# su
# cp bsetroot /usr/bin
# exit
# cd ../..
# rm -rf blackbox-0.70.0beta2

